#: ../../09-document.md:1
msgid "Lazy Todo App — Generating the Project Knowledge Base"
msgstr "Lazy Todo App — 生成项目知识库"

#: ../../09-document.md:5
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "目的"

#: ../../09-document.md:7
msgid ""
"This page explains how to create, update, translate, and publish the Project "
"Knowledge Base (PKB) for `lazy-todo-app`."
msgstr "本页说明如何为 `lazy-todo-app` 创建、更新、翻译并发布项目知识库（PKB）。"

#: ../../09-document.md:9
msgid ""
"In this repository, the PKB lives directly under `doc/`. English Markdown is "
"the source of truth, the content is often drafted or updated with an LLM plus "
"documentation skills, and the published site is built with `Sphinx + MyST + "
"sphinx-intl + Mermaid`."
msgstr ""
"在这个仓库中，PKB 直接位于 `doc/` 下。英文 Markdown 是事实来源，文档内容通常"
"通过 LLM 配合文档技能起草或更新，最终发布站点使用 `Sphinx + MyST + "
"sphinx-intl + Mermaid` 构建。"

#: ../../09-document.md:11
msgid "The current documentation workflow combines:"
msgstr "当前的文档工作流结合了："

#: ../../09-document.md:13
msgid "an LLM to analyze the repo and draft PKB pages"
msgstr "使用 LLM 分析仓库并起草 PKB 页面"

#: ../../09-document.md:14
msgid ""
"skills such as the Project Knowledge Base skill to enforce structure and "
"conventions"
msgstr "使用诸如 Project Knowledge Base skill 之类的技能来约束结构和规范"

#: ../../09-document.md:15
msgid "human review to correct intent, wording, and architectural judgment"
msgstr "通过人工审阅修正文档意图、表述和架构判断"

#: ../../09-document.md:16
msgid "Sphinx tooling to build bilingual HTML output"
msgstr "使用 Sphinx 工具链构建双语 HTML 输出"

#: ../../09-document.md:18
msgid "LLM + Skills Workflow"
msgstr "LLM + Skills 工作流"

#: ../../09-document.md:20
msgid ""
"For this project, PKB pages are typically generated or updated through an "
"LLM-assisted workflow rather than written fully by hand from scratch."
msgstr "在这个项目中，PKB 页面通常通过 LLM 辅助工作流生成或更新，而不是完全从零手工编写。"

#: ../../09-document.md:22
msgid "The practical flow is:"
msgstr "实际流程如下："

#: ../../09-document.md:24
msgid "The LLM reads the repository structure, key configs, and existing docs."
msgstr "LLM 读取仓库结构、关键配置和现有文档。"

#: ../../09-document.md:25
msgid ""
"A documentation skill such as the Project Knowledge Base skill helps "
"structure the output into PKB pages like overview, repo map, architecture, "
"workflows, runbook, and testing docs."
msgstr ""
"像 Project Knowledge Base skill 这样的文档技能会帮助把输出组织成 overview、"
"repo map、architecture、workflows、runbook 和 testing 等 PKB 页面。"

#: ../../09-document.md:26
msgid "The generated Markdown is written into `doc/` as English source pages."
msgstr "生成的 Markdown 会作为英文源页面写入 `doc/`。"

#: ../../09-document.md:27
msgid ""
"A human reviews and edits the result to make sure the \"why\", terminology, "
"and product intent are correct."
msgstr "随后由人工审阅和修改结果，以确保文档中的“为什么”、术语和产品意图都是正确的。"

#: ../../09-document.md:28
msgid ""
"The docs are translated through gettext catalogs and then built into the "
"bilingual site with `Sphinx + MyST + sphinx-intl`."
msgstr "文档通过 gettext catalog 进行翻译，然后使用 `Sphinx + MyST + sphinx-intl` 构建成双语站点。"

#: ../../09-document.md:29
msgid ""
"Mermaid diagrams are used when workflows or architecture benefit from visual "
"explanation."
msgstr "当工作流或架构需要可视化说明时，会使用 Mermaid 图。"

#: ../../09-document.md:31
msgid ""
"This means the PKB should be treated as human-reviewed, AI-assisted "
"documentation. The LLM is responsible for fast synthesis and structure; the "
"human is responsible for validating accuracy, intent, and trade-offs."
msgstr ""
"这意味着 PKB 应该被视为“人工审阅、AI 辅助”的文档。LLM 负责快速归纳和组织结"
"构；人工则负责验证准确性、意图和取舍。"

#: ../../09-document.md:33
msgid "Advisory Auto-Update Loop"
msgstr "告警式自动更新循环"

#: ../../09-document.md:35
msgid ""
"Today, this repository uses an advisory PKB update loop rather than a fully "
"automatic doc-writing bot."
msgstr "当前，这个仓库采用的是告警式 PKB 更新循环，而不是全自动写文档机器人。"

#: ../../09-document.md:37
msgid "The implemented pieces are:"
msgstr "当前已实现的组成部分包括："

#: ../../09-document.md:39
msgid "`scripts/check_pkb_staleness.py` for rule-based PKB impact analysis"
msgstr "`scripts/check_pkb_staleness.py` 用于基于规则的 PKB 影响分析"

#: ../../09-document.md:40
msgid "`npm run pkb:check` for local advisory checks"
msgstr "`npm run pkb:check` 用于本地告警检查"

#: ../../09-document.md:41
msgid "`/.github/workflows/pkb-check.yml` for PR and branch summaries in GitHub Actions"
msgstr "`/.github/workflows/pkb-check.yml` 用于在 GitHub Actions 中生成 PR 和分支摘要"

#: ../../09-document.md:43
msgid "The current loop works like this:"
msgstr "当前循环的工作方式如下："

#: ../../09-document.md:51
msgid ""
"The important design rule is that the checker is deterministic, but the "
"actual documentation refresh still happens through the human-reviewed LLM + "
"skills workflow."
msgstr ""
"一个重要设计原则是：检查器本身应保持确定性，但真正的文档刷新仍然通过“人工审"
"阅的 LLM + skills 工作流”完成。"

#: ../../09-document.md:53
msgid "What the PKB Includes"
msgstr "PKB 包含的内容"

#: ../../09-document.md:65
msgid "Source of Truth"
msgstr "事实来源"

#: ../../09-document.md:59
msgid ""
"Even if a page was generated by an LLM or a skill, the checked-in Markdown "
"files remain the canonical project docs after review."
msgstr "即使某个页面是由 LLM 或 skill 生成的，经过审阅后，仓库中的 Markdown 文件仍然是规范项目文档。"

